<p>ã“ã“ã§æœ€å³è¾ºç¬¬1é …ã¨ç¬¬3é …ã‚’å–ã‚Šå‡ºã—ã¦æ•´ç†ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚ã“ã®ã¨ãã€(9), (16), (17)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\begin{aligned}
&amp;-\nabla \left\{\frac{v_{1z}}{\Lambda} P_0 - C_s^2 \rho_0 (\nabla \cdot \mathbf{v}_1) \right\} + g \left\{ - v_{1z} \frac{\rho_0}{\Lambda} + \rho_0 (\nabla \cdot \mathbf{v}_1) \right\} \mathbf{e}_z \\
